Investigation of the 1 failing WS3D test (`Phase6RigRegistryTests.Constants_defines_the_actor_rig_registry_entries`) confirmed it was **pre-existing from commit `a717fad`** (codex plate-81 fix: correct actor rig mapping). The test was added at `ea14ab8` but never updated when `Constants.cs` refactored from inline `["human"]` syntax to an `AddRigGroup` helper. Same failure reproduces when checking out `a717fad` and running tests in isolation. **Not introduced by any merge in this session.**

